// This file is intentionally not picked up by vitest (extension is
// `.test.ts.skip`, not `.test.ts`). It is the scaffold for the Day
// 12-13 work item in `.local/tasks/freeze-14-day.md`: real-PG
// integration tests that prove company A cannot read company B's
// rows over the actual HTTP surface.
//
// Why parked: the existing test suite is 100% static-analysis; the
// repo has no docker-compose / Testcontainers integration to spin up
