// review surface (CI runner image, secrets, seed strategy). Capturing
// the intended shape here keeps the contract visible.
//
// Day 12 implementation outline:
//   1. `tests/integration/postgres/docker-compose.yml` — pg:16-alpine,
//      seeded once per CI job via the existing `db/bootstrap.sh`
//      + `db/dump-seed.sh` pipeline.
//   2. Vitest `globalSetup` that:
//        - boots the compose stack
//        - runs migrations from `artifacts/api-server/migrations/`
//        - inserts two companies (A, B) via the same seed scripts
//        - inserts one owner + one regular user per company
//        - mints two JWT tokens (tokenA, tokenB) using the same
//          signing key as authMiddleware
//   3. The test below uses `supertest` against the real `app.ts`
//      Express handler.

